  "text": "We describe the key computational steps in the ENVE methodology and evaluate its performance using two matched tumor/normal WES datasets, an in-house WES dataset of predominantly late-stage, MSS AA CRCs (N = 30) [CITATION_1] , and a Caucasian MSS CRC WES dataset obtained from TCGA (TCGA CRC, N = 77) (See \"Methods\" and Additional file 1: Table S1 ). A subset of these TCGA cases consisting of predominantly late-stage cancers (N = 30) was used to further assess differences in sCNAs in CRCs arising in AA versus Caucasian ethnicities.",
